Dear Monday Bar family, We’d like to tell you that the long awaited after-movie from Monday Bar Black & White Cruise, May 17-19 is now out on YouTube. Filmed and produced by Lyione Media. A bit longer than usual, but a lot of fun and well worth the wait! Turn up the volume and go back a few months in time..  <https://youtu.be/C2okiKfKrlQ> WATCH IT HERE!  <https://youtu.be/C2okiKfKrlQ> Reminder about passport and National ID!! Our 60 Cruise Jubilee is quickly approaching and we’d like once again to remind you about to make sure that you bring a Passport or National ID card. Regular ID or Drivers License are NOT valid identification. And please check the expiration date. ALL CABINS ARE SOLD OUT - But there are still empty beds to fill All cabins are now SOLD OUT, but there is still capacity to fill booked cabins with more people (up to 4 persons per cabin in standard A, B and E class). So if you know someone who have booked only 1-2 persons in one cabin, they should be able to get an upgrade for an extra fee. You should speak to the booking office about this and have your booking reference ready. Call +46-8-666 33 33 or send an email to: kundservice@tallinksilja.com Find empty cabins in our Facebook Group - but beware of FAKE SELLERS! There are always people with booked cabins who can’t go for different reasons. But also those who have an empty bed to sell. Follow our Facebook group and the event. But be very aware of FAKE SELLERS. https://www.facebook.com/groups/mondaybar/ ALWAYS check with the booking office that the booking is genuine, and NEVER transfer money until the change of names have been made. Dress theme: COLOUR EXPLOSION People have asked if we will have a dress theme at The Last Cruise in October. The previous theme was Black & White, so now we're doing the opposite, COLOUR EXPLOSION!! Our decor will of course be adapted accordingly. And Dominika at C.U.M. is of course willing to help those of you who want some inspiration. MONDAY BAR CRUISE No 60 JUBILEE - THE LAST CRUISE Friday-Sunday October 6-8, 2023 (2 nights - 41h) M/S Baltic Queen Stockholm-Tallinn-Stockholm Cruise times Departure, Stockholm Tallink-Silja ferry terminal, Värtahamnen Friday, October 6, 17:30 (5:30 PM), local Swedish time Arrival, Tallinn Tallink D-terminal Saturday October 7, 10:45 (10:45 AM), local Estonian time (+1 hour) Departure, Tallinn Tallink D-terminal Saturday October 7, 18:00 (6 PM), local Estonian time (+1 hour) Arrival, Stockholm Tallink-Silja ferry terminal, Värtahamnen Sunday October 8, 10:30 (10:30 AM), local Swedish time Age limit: 18 years when boarding. Cabin prices starting at SEK 1420 per person CRUISE HOMEPAGE  <https://www.mondaybar.com/mondaybar-no-60-jubilee-cruise-2023?ss_source=sscampaigns&ss_campaign_id=6506ee04bfa2ee0835cfed18&ss_email_id=6506f7b4bfa2ee0835d08462&ss_campaign_name=Newsflash%E2%9A%A1%EF%B8%8FMonday+Bar+B%26W+after-movie+%2B+reminders&ss_campaign_sent_date=2023-09-17T12%3A58%3A11Z> FACEBOOK EVENT  <https://www.facebook.com/events/645537783591634/>  <https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBTe8_DMsFC3HYqEg4suMxg>  <http://facebook.com/mondaybar>  <http://instagram.com/mondaybar>  <http://twitter.com/mondaybar> © Monday Bar, 1992-2023 Box 2254, SE-10316 Stockholm, Sweden Unsubscribe  <https://campaign-preferences.com/unsubscribe/gBWjAMV_zp77ls9f-renhO3kb4V1fAR8p3ColcYWjU0kBw6DKM5Su1DCRFUER8zD1opkeYgwXJVi60GtogPvhrSPeBRsq5FE_PuKqMvbO6rm2hudPL0Y3QJSHh2kOs-uL2Df2b_Nxq1SB6wxwOqNhBqzRD67xSgY6hIdUddAhGM84pCf3Qv5VWo-yGmwy_wEf0aEUWc8rXBQPP2DUxqXkf9f5QHTUiJIzqbubIvQ5FUbV0qMr2ELNhz8PvnlrmkX2E4Zsl2GH1Gl3czYueqe7fcT04P5S9qQ8LpsUa6Xrm2yyDYgKKfTdFBvA5rXpZpanmJaP_5bB9PDLbZJGdppwYy8uLJBWFGNKEAyIGB12M8ICX6GU73aKBI=>